description:
Tika Sumpter [Mixed-ish, Gossip Girl, Ride Along, What’s Your Number?] reconnects with Anna to talk about working together, hiding from your kids, the optimism of Los Angeles, wining people over, Footloose, artificial syrup and more. Later in the episode Anna is joined by psychotherapist and author of The Atlantic’s “Dear Therapist” column Lori Gottlieb to offer some qualified and Unqualified advice to a listener.

For more from Lori visit her website lorigottlieb.com
